s, vault, and balance beam, while rhythmic gymnastics takes the form of individual floor exercises akin to dance routines.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Artistic gymnastics\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"the parallel bars\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"balance beam\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"rhythmic gymnastics\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"individual floor exercises\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 900}, {\"ngram\": \"dance routines\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gymnastics competition will take place throughout the Games, with the first medal events taking place on 29 July for men's artistic gymnastics.\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gymnastics competition\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"the first medal events\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"29 July\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"men's artistic gymnastics\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trampoline and rhythmic gymnastics will not begin until 2 and 8 August, respectively.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trampoline\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"2 and 8 August\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"American sensationSimone Bileswill make her return to full Olympic competition this summer after dropping out of the Tokyo games, citing amental block known as the 'twisties'.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\":